    "Efficient, biologically accurate, modular models are becoming increasingly important for edge computing and deployment in resource-constrained environments.",
    "To evaluate the different modules in the tiered pipeline in this context, we measured accuracy and GPU energy usage for each module.",
    "We then evaluated the biological validity of results based on treatment effects using mixed effects modeling.",
    "To evaluate and compare the two state estimation modules, we calculated the coefficient of determination (R 2) and root mean squared error (RMSE) for each fold, training and inference time, and energy usage for model training/validation and inference.",
    "Per-nutrient R² and global R 2 values were calculated for each fold, from which the average and standard deviation across the manual cross validation 27 folds were determined."
